Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At a certain hot spring, there is an inn where liars gather
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:10.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I kinda forgot about this, it's been a while
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:12.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yes true
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:14.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,When was the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:16.40,Hosei,,0,0,0,,1 year? 1 year
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:22.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh it's been a year? Hmm I don't really remember much...except Yamasaki really sucked
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:24.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's as much as I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to explain the rules for Liar's Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They pick a card with small, medium or massive written on it along with someone's name. That person nominates someone else to tell a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever is nominated must maintain the lie until it's time to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:46.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I think it would be better to have an audience for this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:50.32,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yeah for sure, it would be better if there was an audience
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:53.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well the staff here aren't that bad
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:54.04,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You guys are depressing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:56.24,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So god damn heavy hearted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:01:00.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They're depressing, and they're old men, they way they think
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:01.08,Hosei,,0,0,0,,They think like old men!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:04.12,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:04.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They can't keep up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:06.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah for real
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:08.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:11.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ah so Endo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo nominates someone to tell a massive lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Endo picks a massive lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:18.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But a massive lie right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:19.96,Hamada,,0,0,0,,A massive lie is hard to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:25.68,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is something that really surprised me when I heard it \N I was eating dinner with some people,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:29.68,Endo,,0,0,0,,And someone said something that made me go "Did that really happen?!" Matsumoto-san
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:36.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,Did a meteorite really fall on your family's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It was a pretty long time ago though
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:40.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,A while ago? When
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:41.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I think it's been 7 years
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:42.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,7 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:45.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There were a ton of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:47.72,Endo,,0,0,0,,Oh, it wasn't just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:50.19,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,904)}One of them fell right on my mom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:53.24,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Wait if it hit your mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:57.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,On my mom, here, it smacked her like BAAAM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:59.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,But that would kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:00.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:02.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We were all watching Kōhaku on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:07.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,My mom- Was it this side or this side? I can't remember for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:11.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It hit like BAAAM \N And she went like OWWW
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.20,Endo,,0,0,0,,Surely Ow isn't enough
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:14.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It was amazing actually
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:16.48,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Were you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:19.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We were playing Domino (Shichi Narabe)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,7 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:24.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And my mom's hand stopped right at the 6
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:27.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And we were talking about whether that was a foul or not
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:32.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,My mom refused to play the 6
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I really remember that moment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:39.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I said "Who did this?!" and then it hit her like BAAAM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:45.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And then when her cards fell I saw it was my mom's fault
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:48.68,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Ah she was holding it back after all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:50.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah it was all mom's fault
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:56.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Basically everyone was really pissed off about the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:03:02.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So like we had a talk like "It's bad to ruin the fun like that" ... and it's become a great story in our household
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Mmm.  Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:09.24,Endo,,0,0,0,,I understand. I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,Sorry Matsumoto-san, your sweating is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:14.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Sorry, umm, uhh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:20.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Even though you gave me a massive lie...I'm sorry I turned it into something so small
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:26.89,Credits,,0,0,0,,Timed & Typeset by Kedomas\NTranslation by senor_wristband
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6EFDFF&}Fully Improvised Liar's Inn\NThey must maintain the lie no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fully Improvised! Liar's Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They pick a card with small, medium or massive written on it along with someone's name. That person nominates someone else to tell a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever is nominated must maintain the lie until it's time to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Alright here I go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.56,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's you again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:04:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo nominates someone to tell a small lie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:04.48,Endo,,0,0,0,,Tanaka, are you alright? Your rib is broken right now right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:07.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,Are you good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:13.08,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Ah, now that you mention it, it makes it hard to continue
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.24,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Is it a crack, or is it broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:17.00,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's broken
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:19.44,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It's totally broken? I don't think I could hold the pain back for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:22.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh? He's not really speaking that loudly either
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:26.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He was speaking pretty loudly just earlier though
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Could you try making a loud noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:29.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Wow that hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.92,Endo,,0,0,0,,It resonates?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:32.04,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,If I'm not lying
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.64,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"If I'm not lying"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You're enduring it you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:39.52,Endo,,0,0,0,,What did you do that made this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.96,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I kinda started doing Martial Arts recently
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,That sounds like a true story
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I didn't know about that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:50.64,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was in a state of no exercise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:53.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,"A state of no exercise"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:59.08,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I don't really do any exercise, which I thought isn't good. So I started doing Martial Arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:01.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.72,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Mixed Martial Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:05.04,Endo,,0,0,0,,Like what kind of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:08.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:11.16,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.56,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Mixed Martial Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I do know some stuff about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.00,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Oh yes Matsumoto-san you do martial arts right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.16,0:05:18.34,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,In Ebisu (District of Tokyo)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ebisu already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:21.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Ebisu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.68,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You don't mean the location, but the Organization right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.50,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Organization? Oh they said they're not associated with any organization
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:32.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well forget about the organization, what's the place called?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:35.38,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It says "Ebisu Mixed Gym" on the sign
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:38.28,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Ebisu Mixed Gym, that's where I go
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:41.67,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Who are you getting to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:42.16,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I, uh, my Missus
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.88,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Missus? Your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.04,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Then just do it at home. You don't need to go to Ebisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:50.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You don't need to go to Ebisu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:54.32,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Does she have any qualifications? Your wi-Missus
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.40,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Wi-Missus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:57.92,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes she does, she got her qualifications a while ago
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:06:00.12,Endo,,0,0,0,,Your wife has a trainer's license?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.88,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes yes yes she has a trainer's license
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.88,Endo,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it hurt to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.88,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's fine it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.48,Endo,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:09.04,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's fine, this is my job after all
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:10.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:13.72,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I can't really go "Ow Ow" here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah of course
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:16.64,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,So I'm forcing myself, for lack of a better word
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:19.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Your wife does it too then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.32,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, she does it too
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:23.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It must be awful to get into quarrels with her
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.24,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Oh no no yes, just one hit is all it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:27.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh she hits you? Yeah that makes sense
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.24,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,She just high kicks me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.80,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:32.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Why did she high kick you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:36.74,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,... Well to sum it up, I had an affair
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.72,Endo,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.34,Endo,,0,0,0,,You cheated on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:47.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, in some sense, a high kick to get it over with is good
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:51.18,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes exactly, after the kick she forgave me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,Here I go
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san nominates someone to tell a medium lie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:55.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san's medium
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:57.96,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san's medium
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:01.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:04.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I heard this, Yamasaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:10.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Yamasaki found some STAP cells
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,244)}STAP was a proposed method of generating stem cells discovered in Japan that was later found to use falsified data in its report
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.36,Endo,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:18.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There's no way that's true... Not after everything we know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:18.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Even though they said they don't exist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But apparently it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:25.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,My wife found out after Yamasaki's wife sent her a text
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:31.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,She sent like "My husband found some STAP cells!" \N With a laughing emoji
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:35.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The sweating laughing emoji
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:39.76,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Man I told her not to tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's a lie right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:45.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,This is, this is the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:51.64,Hosei,,0,0,0,,But I kept it secret, and it became a big thing, like the Japanese scientists and stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:53.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There are scientists outside of Japan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:55.44,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is a major global discovery
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:08:02.28,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I told her, you know, this will become a big deal scientifically. \N I did tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:06.84,Endo,,0,0,0,,But isn't it a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah if it's true
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:14.56,Hosei,,0,0,0,,When Obok*ta-san announced that they exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:21.32,Hosei,,0,0,0,,If she's saying STAP cells really exist, then let's go out and try to find some
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:24.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You went on a journey to find STAP cells?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.64,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,But that was disproven right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.04,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I found some
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.72,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,How did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:37.24,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Uh, you know, I was shocked myself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:44.68,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I was so shocked ... I just kept walking
