Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:53.64,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I uh, I made it all the way to Kyoto
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:55.96,Endo,,0,0,0,,Why'd you go to Kyoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:09:00.32,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Well cause, it's an ancient city, and they have lots of temples
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,By yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:04.52,Hosei,,0,0,0,,By myself, of course
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:07.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,To find a new discovery, he goes to an ancient city instead
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:07.28,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yeah instead
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:14.24,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to show that STAP cells are nothing new,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:18.44,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,But they are a new thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.98,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:23.92,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So I was just walking through Kyoto, and I went to a temple first and asked them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:29.36,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"Excuse me, have you ever heard anything about STAP cells?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:34.13,Endo,,0,0,0,,You asked like you were looking for a missing person?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Missing person...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is so messed up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.78,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Well, in the end-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:38.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You might as well ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:40.48,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I might as well ask. I really had nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:46.52,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"Excuse me, have you heard anything about STAP cells? In this area"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:52.72,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"Is there nothing about that from the past?" \N "No"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:56.16,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I said "Oh is that so"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:10:00.68,Hosei,,0,0,0,,At around the 8th temple I went to though,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:06.32,Hosei,,0,0,0,,They said "Why are you searching for STAP cells?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.68,Endo,,0,0,0,,They knew about it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:13.64,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"Well actually, I really like STAP cells..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,You like STAP cells?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:19.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"So I'm looking for them"
