Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Be honest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.84,Endo,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:33.64,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It was ... behind the Jizo statue
