Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Enough already
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:45.72,Endo,,0,0,0,,You found STAP cells behind the Jizo statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:46.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.40,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Wow, in such a place
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:48.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto nominates someone to tell a massive lie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:52.33,Hosei,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.33,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:56.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I heard Hamada is genuinely the Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,TN: Kamen Rider is a superhero
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I thought he was supposed to be a cyborg
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But this is for real
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:09.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Your wife said it on a TV show in Osaka
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.95,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yomiuri I think it was
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:17.32,Endo,,0,0,0,,Really? Well she did reveal it in Kansai
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:20.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why did she say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:24.44,Endo,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:24.44,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:30.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So it's real then? What I don't understand is why you became a Cyborg
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:36.53,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well it's the same reason as Hongo Takeshi (Kamen Rider's protaganist)
