Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:40.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No, he was kidnapped by Shocker (evil organisation)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He was kidnapped by Shocker
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.32,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Woke up strapped down like this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:45.42,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Eh? You were kidnapped by Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What else would it have been!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:56.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,"When"? ... I've kept it secret for so long I think I've forgotten \N Maybe grade 8?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:58.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So young!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:01.04,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,You got caught in grade 8?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Before the middle school trip
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.76,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Wow they caught you back then
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But you came on that trip right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:10.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I did, I managed to convince them to let me, somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:12.24,Endo,,0,0,0,,Oh you asked them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:16.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,But they told me they just finished so "Don't transform at all"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:20.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They said there's still some parts they didn't attach yet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.72,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Didn't attach?
