Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Like properly you know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.36,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Oh not properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:31.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They didn't attach the cyborg parts properly, so if I transform now they'll come off
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:38.80,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So on that trip, well you were there, we went to different places, and sang and danced like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:42.80,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I couldn't move like that, they told me side to side movements like that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:45.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You couldn't even move side to side?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:49.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Cause it's like, my hip would slip and return, slip and return
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.80,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:55.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So I didn't even like doing this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Maybe I wasn't developed enough in middle school
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.92,Endo,,0,0,0,,Have you transformed a bunch of times before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:06.64,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well one time I did think "I should be fine" and did try to transform
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You tried? How do you transform?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:14.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well they didn't tell me anything, so of course I just tried saying "Transform!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:19.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,But it barely did anything. My upper body was the same, but my lower body went like *cyborg noises*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:22.76,Endo,,0,0,0,,Eh your lower body? What happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It looked sort of like compression pants
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.12,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's not very cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:31.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You don't know what it was though right? It looked like Egashira?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:32.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I didn't really know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:38.64,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah, I thought something would happen to my upper body. But it was lame, it was just compression pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.96,Endo,,0,0,0,,Oh you were just normal from the top
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:42.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I just thought "this sucks, I don't want to be seen like this"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's just embarrassing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's just embarassing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:47.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,"Enough" I said "Nope!" and *cyborg noises*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.88,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,You said "Nope" and it went back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:54.22,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So you didn't fight any monsters?
