Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Person to person?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:04.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If you train well then you can get good in about a month
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:08.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,But my physique wasn't good. And I had side effects.
