Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.36,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:45.78,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,If I ever talk about this, people go "Are you serious?" or "That's so weird!", so I've never talked about it before but,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:50.76,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,But, yes, if I had to say so, it is true
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:54.88,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,In my past life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:16:00.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was, well my appearance was mostly the same, I was still tall
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:05.84,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,But yeah I was a woman that had this same sort of look
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Pretty tall
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.48,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:10.96,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,A 181cm tall woman
