Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.04,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Ar- Argentina
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.68,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,Tanaka Naoki used to be Argentina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:29.36,Hosei,,0,0,0,,An Argentinian named Argentina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:31.94,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Isn't that strange? Argentinian Argentina, that's like being named Nippon Tarou
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.32,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, my name was Argentina
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.14,Hosei,,0,0,0,,What kind of job did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.48,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Umm
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:42.28,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Well basically, I was a daughter, I didn't do any work
