Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:52.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well that's possible for a girl right? Not working part time or a job or anything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:55.20,Hosei,,0,0,0,,But you did work a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I didn't, I wasn't suited for that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:58.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was free, I really did nothing, I lived a life of no worries
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You were a noblewoman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.92,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I was a noblewoman
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:01.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So your parents were...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:03.00,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, my parents were-
