Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:06.88,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,My parents, were on the street corner doing real estate
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Why mention the street corner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.84,Endo,,0,0,0,,The street corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:13.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Forget about the street corner
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:17.84,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,They did real estate, they didn't own that much land, but they did have some
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:19.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Real estate huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:22.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You didn't have any siblings?
